CUdpDriver udpDriver(AT91C_BASE_UDP, AT91C_ID_UDP, AT91C_PMC_UDP) [static]

Default driver when an UDP controller is present on a chip. Note that CUdpDriver implementation is masked i.e. it is private to this module it exports only its usb driver interface as sDefautlUsbDriver.
